I have been listening again and again to this song for years!
Great mix of these 3 magical voices and the perfectly fitted instrumental musical behind it.
Nitin Sawhney surely knows how to gather great talents.
It is too bad that it is not available in spotify, but in the other hand I would listen to it too much :)
Congratulations from France!

Et j'espère les voir un jour ! Un grand grand merci.
